ORIGINAL WORK

The firectl command-line tool was originally created by Amazon.com, Inc.
as part of the Firecracker project for managing Firecracker microVMs.

Repository: https://github.com/anubhavg-icpl/agni

---

GUI IMPLEMENTATION

The graphical user interface (GUI) for Agni was developed by Anubhav Gain
as a derivative work, adding the following features:

- Web-based GUI with Svelte + TypeScript frontend
- REST API server for programmatic access
- Multi-VM management dashboard
- Real-time log streaming via WebSocket
- VM metrics visualization
- Configuration template management
- JWT-based authentication system
- BoltDB persistence layer

The GUI can be enabled by running: agni --gui

